PrecisRegulations Amending the NOTICES OF UNINSURED DEPOSITS REGULATIONS to the extent that a wholesale bank operating out of a location that it shares with a retail bank will be required to disclose, both orally and in writing, the fact that its business is separate and distinct from that of the retail bank and that deposits are not insured by the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation.
